Description: "Mario Kart - Lite Game\r\n\r\nFlow\r\n Start Menu -> Select Cup Menu -> Go to kart selection and then start with the first Track in that Cup, when the first Track completes, the Lobby will be displayed to allow different kart selection, after this the second Track will start and this continues to the last trak and start again from the first trak.\r\n\r\nIf you want to race in a different Cup you should start the game and select the other Cup."
